Package cmput301w16t08.scaling_pancake.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Deserializer
    Deserializer is a class meant to translate between JSON strings used by the ElasticsearchController and User, Instrument, and Bid objects.
    PrePostActionWrapper
    PrePostActionWrapper allows views to pass in their own specific methods to be called during the onPreExecute() and onPostExecute() calls of the SearchInstrumentTask in ElasticSearchController.
    Serializer
    Serializer is a class meant to translate between Users, Instruments, and Bids, and JSON strings that can be used by the ElasticsearchController.
